-- Shanghai Volkswagen General Manager Dies in Traffic Accident, Xinhua Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-19T04:37:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/shanghai-volkswagen-general-manager-dies-in-traffic-accident-xinhua-says.html

          
          
             The general manager of Shanghai
Volkswagen Automotive Co. was killed in a traffic accident along
with three other people, the official Xinhua News Agency
reported, citing the company.  
 The accident occured July 17 during a company event in
Gansu province, Xinhua reported.  
